Package Description
com.github.dylon.liblevenshtein.collection
Collections and things that belong in collections, such as symmetric, immutable pairs, DAWGs and max-heaps.

Interfaces and implementations for various DAWG structures.

Various utilities specifically related to Levenshtein distance, such as distance metrics, transducers, and classes for constructing them.

Various implementations of Levenshtein distance.

com.github.dylon.liblevenshtein.levenshtein.factory
Factories that build things pertaining directly with Levenshtein distance, such as those which build transducers and distance metrics.

(De)Serialization utilities for various interchange formats.
